title: Tumi Alpha Bravo Luke Roll-Top Leather Backpack 92388 - Overview
description:
Tumi Alpha Bravo Luke Roll-Top Leather Backpack - 92388 - DARK BROWN
http://www.abt.com/product/92806/Tumi-92388DARKBROWN.html?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=video&utm_campaign=092388DB2_20160302

Handsomely reimagined in rich leather this generously-sized roll top backpack tote was designed to be stuffed. Secure your phone tablet and laptop plus papers or files and enough clothes to get you through the weekend. Comfortable padded backpack straps. Top zip closure
Features:
• Primary Material:
o Leather 
• Laptop Dimensions:
o Fits: up to 15
o H: 15.75
o W: 12.25
o D: 1.5
• Exterior Features:
o Leather top carry handle
o Adjustable shoulder strap
o Roll-top fold over main compartment
o Zip entry to main compartment
o Multiple front zip pockets
o 1 side zip pocket
o Main and back compartment separated by zipper
• Interior Features:
o iPad pocket
o 15 laptop compartment
o 2 open pockets
o 1 media pocket
o 1 zipped pocket
o 2 business card pockets
o 1 pen loop
o Key leash
